title: Was Raphael Warnock Arrested at the Capitol in 2017?
subtitle: A photo of police surrounding Warnock at the U.S. Capitol drew comparisons to violent pro-Trump riots on Jan. 6, 2021.
author: Bethania Palma
vclaim: Rev. Raphael Warnock was arrested while praying during a demonstration at the U.S. Capitol in 2017.
